name: Protect Me From What I Want
wikiSummary: Brian Moloko told Kerrang! that this song “was inspired by the conceptual artist Jenny Holzer.” He added: “It is really a discourse with myself about my self destructive behaviour.” (Source Protect Me From What I Want Songfacts).
